Release 1.2.0
  New
    > Added option for extension to reopen on page refresh
    > Settings are reloaded across page refresh
    > Canvases can now be captured when page is loaded
    > Improved canvas highlighting when selecting canvas
    > Canvases in nested iframes now highlight correctly

Release 1.1.1
  New
    > Capture video from canvases in nested iframes
    > Set delay before starting capture
    > Set timeout to stop capturing after certain duration
    > Highlight canvases in page to easily identify them
    > Minimize the display to see more of the captured page

